1568 }
1569 }
1570
1571 // set approximate max bounding box (take in account also the tool marker)
1572 m_max_bounding_box = m_paths_bounding_box;
1573 m_max_bounding_box.merge(m_paths_bounding_box.max + m_sequential_view.marker.get_bounding_box().size().z() * Vec3d::UnitZ());
1574
1575 if (wxGetApp().is_editor())
1576 m_contained_in_bed = wxGetApp().plater()->build_volume().all_paths_inside(gcode_result, m_paths_bounding_box);
1577
1578 m_cog.reset();
1579
1580 m_sequential_view.gcode_ids.clear();
1581 for (size_t i = 0; i < gcode_result.moves.size(); ++i) {
1582 const GCodeProcessorResult::MoveVertex& move = gcode_result.moves[i];
1583 if (move.type != EMoveType::Seam)
1584 m_sequential_view.gcode_ids.push_back(move.gcode_id);
1585 }
1586
1587 bool account_for_volumetric_rate = m_view_type == EViewType::VolumetricRate;
1588
1589 std::vector<MultiVertexBuffer> vertices(m_buffers.size());
1590 std::vector<MultiIndexBuffer> indices(m_buffers.size());
1591 std::vector<InstanceBuffer> instances(m_buffers.size());
1592 std::vector<InstanceIdBuffer> instances_ids(m_buffers.size());
1593 std::vector<InstancesOffsets> instances_offsets(m_buffers.size());
1594 std::vector<float> options_zs;
1595
1596 std::vector<size_t> biased_seams_ids;
1597
1598 // toolpaths data -> extract vertices from result
1599 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_moves_count; ++i) {
1600 const GCodeProcessorResult::MoveVertex& curr = gcode_result.moves[i];
1601 if (curr.type == EMoveType::Seam)
1602 biased_seams_ids.push_back(i - biased_seams_ids.size() - 1);
1603
1604 const size_t move_id = i - biased_seams_ids.size();
1605
1606 // skip first vertex
1607 if (i == 0)
1608 continue;
1609
1610 const GCodeProcessorResult::MoveVertex& prev = gcode_result.moves[i - 1];
1611
1612 if (curr.type == EMoveType::Extrude &&
1613 curr.extrusion_role != GCodeExtrusionRole::Skirt &&
1614 curr.extrusion_role != GCodeExtrusionRole::SupportMaterial &&
1615 curr.extrusion_role != GCodeExtrusionRole::SupportMaterialInterface &&
1616 curr.extrusion_role != GCodeExtrusionRole::WipeTower &&
1617 curr.extrusion_role != GCodeExtrusionRole::Custom) {
1618 const Vec3d curr_pos = curr.position.cast<double>();
1619 const Vec3d prev_pos = prev.position.cast<double>();
1620 m_cog.add_segment(curr_pos, prev_pos, curr.mm3_per_mm * (curr_pos - prev_pos).norm());
1621 }
1622
1623 // update progress dialog
1624 ++progress_count;
1625 if (progress_dialog != nullptr && progress_count % progress_threshold == 0) {
1626 progress_dialog->Update(int(100.0f * float(i) / (2.0f * float(m_moves_count))),
1627 _L("Generating vertex buffer") + ": " + wxNumberFormatter::ToString(100.0 * double(i) / double(m_moves_count), 0, wxNumberFormatter::Style_None) + "%");
1628 progress_dialog->Fit();
1629 progress_count = 0;
1630 }
1631
1632 const unsigned char id = buffer_id(curr.type);
1633 TBuffer& t_buffer = m_buffers[id];
1634 MultiVertexBuffer& v_multibuffer = vertices[id];
1635 InstanceBuffer& inst_buffer = instances[id];
1636 InstanceIdBuffer& inst_id_buffer = instances_ids[id];
1637 InstancesOffsets& inst_offsets = instances_offsets[id];
1638
1639 // ensure there is at least one vertex buffer
1640 if (v_multibuffer.empty())
1641 v_multibuffer.push_back(VertexBuffer());
1642
1643 // if adding the vertices for the current segment exceeds the threshold size of the current vertex buffer
1644 // add another vertex buffer
1645 size_t vertices_size_to_add = (t_buffer.render_primitive_type == TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::BatchedModel) ? t_buffer.model.data.vertices_size_bytes() : t_buffer.max_vertices_per_segment_size_bytes();
1646 if (v_multibuffer.back().size() * sizeof(float) > t_buffer.vertices.max_size_bytes() - vertices_size_to_add) {
1647 v_multibuffer.push_back(VertexBuffer());
1648 if (t_buffer.render_primitive_type == TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::Triangle) {
1649 Path& last_path = t_buffer.paths.back();
1650 if (prev.type == curr.type && last_path.matches(curr, account_for_volumetric_rate))
1651 last_path.add_sub_path(prev, static_cast<unsigned int>(v_multibuffer.size()) - 1, 0, move_id - 1);
1652 }
1653 }
1654
1655 VertexBuffer& v_buffer = v_multibuffer.back();
1656
1657 switch (t_buffer.render_primitive_type)
1658 {
1659 case TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::Line: { add_vertices_as_line(prev, curr, v_buffer); break; }
1660 case TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::Triangle: { add_vertices_as_solid(prev, curr, t_buffer, static_cast<unsigned int>(v_multibuffer.size()) - 1, v_buffer, move_id, account_for_volumetric_rate); break; }
1661 case TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::InstancedModel:
1662 {
1663 add_model_instance(curr, inst_buffer, inst_id_buffer, move_id);
1664 inst_offsets.push_back(prev.position - curr.position);
1665#if ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1666 ++m_statistics.instances_count;
1667#endif // ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1668 break;
1669 }
1670 case TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::BatchedModel:
1671 {
1672 add_vertices_as_model_batch(curr, t_buffer.model.data, v_buffer, inst_buffer, inst_id_buffer, move_id);
1673 inst_offsets.push_back(prev.position - curr.position);
1674#if ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1675 ++m_statistics.batched_count;
1676#endif // ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1677 break;
1678 }
1679 }
1680
1681 // collect options zs for later use
1682 if (curr.type == EMoveType::Pause_Print || curr.type == EMoveType::Custom_GCode) {
1683 const float* const last_z = options_zs.empty() ? nullptr : &options_zs.back();
1684 if (last_z == nullptr || curr.position[2] < *last_z - EPSILON || *last_z + EPSILON < curr.position[2])
1685 options_zs.emplace_back(curr.position[2]);
1686 }
1687 }

1689 // smooth toolpaths corners for the given TBuffer using triangles
1690 auto smooth_triangle_toolpaths_corners = [&gcode_result, &biased_seams_ids](const TBuffer& t_buffer, MultiVertexBuffer& v_multibuffer) {
1691 auto extract_position_at = [](const VertexBuffer& vertices, size_t offset) {
1692 return Vec3f(vertices[offset + 0], vertices[offset + 1], vertices[offset + 2]);
1693 };
1694 auto update_position_at = [](VertexBuffer& vertices, size_t offset, const Vec3f& position) {
1695 vertices[offset + 0] = position.x();
1696 vertices[offset + 1] = position.y();
1697 vertices[offset + 2] = position.z();
1698 };
1699 auto match_right_vertices = [&](const Path::Sub_Path& prev_sub_path, const Path::Sub_Path& next_sub_path,
1700 size_t curr_s_id, size_t vertex_size_floats, const Vec3f& displacement_vec) {
1701 if (&prev_sub_path == &next_sub_path) { // previous and next segment are both contained into to the same vertex buffer
1702 VertexBuffer& vbuffer = v_multibuffer[prev_sub_path.first.b_id];
1703 // offset into the vertex buffer of the next segment 1st vertex
1704 const size_t next_1st_offset = (prev_sub_path.last.s_id - curr_s_id) * 6 * vertex_size_floats;
1705 // offset into the vertex buffer of the right vertex of the previous segment
1706 const size_t prev_right_offset = prev_sub_path.last.i_id - next_1st_offset - 3 * vertex_size_floats;
1707 // new position of the right vertices
1708 const Vec3f shared_vertex = extract_position_at(vbuffer, prev_right_offset) + displacement_vec;
1709 // update previous segment
1710 update_position_at(vbuffer, prev_right_offset, shared_vertex);
1711 // offset into the vertex buffer of the right vertex of the next segment
1712 const size_t next_right_offset = next_sub_path.last.i_id - next_1st_offset;
1713 // update next segment
1714 update_position_at(vbuffer, next_right_offset, shared_vertex);
1715 }
1716 else { // previous and next segment are contained into different vertex buffers
1717 VertexBuffer& prev_vbuffer = v_multibuffer[prev_sub_path.first.b_id];
1718 VertexBuffer& next_vbuffer = v_multibuffer[next_sub_path.first.b_id];
1719 // offset into the previous vertex buffer of the right vertex of the previous segment
1720 const size_t prev_right_offset = prev_sub_path.last.i_id - 3 * vertex_size_floats;
1721 // new position of the right vertices
1722 const Vec3f shared_vertex = extract_position_at(prev_vbuffer, prev_right_offset) + displacement_vec;
1723 // update previous segment
1724 update_position_at(prev_vbuffer, prev_right_offset, shared_vertex);
1725 // offset into the next vertex buffer of the right vertex of the next segment
1726 const size_t next_right_offset = next_sub_path.first.i_id + 1 * vertex_size_floats;
1727 // update next segment
1728 update_position_at(next_vbuffer, next_right_offset, shared_vertex);
1729 }
1730 };
1731 auto match_left_vertices = [&](const Path::Sub_Path& prev_sub_path, const Path::Sub_Path& next_sub_path,
1732 size_t curr_s_id, size_t vertex_size_floats, const Vec3f& displacement_vec) {
1733 if (&prev_sub_path == &next_sub_path) { // previous and next segment are both contained into to the same vertex buffer
1734 VertexBuffer& vbuffer = v_multibuffer[prev_sub_path.first.b_id];
1735 // offset into the vertex buffer of the next segment 1st vertex
1736 const size_t next_1st_offset = (prev_sub_path.last.s_id - curr_s_id) * 6 * vertex_size_floats;
1737 // offset into the vertex buffer of the left vertex of the previous segment
1738 const size_t prev_left_offset = prev_sub_path.last.i_id - next_1st_offset - 1 * vertex_size_floats;
1739 // new position of the left vertices
1740 const Vec3f shared_vertex = extract_position_at(vbuffer, prev_left_offset) + displacement_vec;
1741 // update previous segment
1742 update_position_at(vbuffer, prev_left_offset, shared_vertex);
1743 // offset into the vertex buffer of the left vertex of the next segment
1744 const size_t next_left_offset = next_sub_path.last.i_id - next_1st_offset + 1 * vertex_size_floats;
1745 // update next segment
1746 update_position_at(vbuffer, next_left_offset, shared_vertex);
1747 }
1748 else { // previous and next segment are contained into different vertex buffers
1749 VertexBuffer& prev_vbuffer = v_multibuffer[prev_sub_path.first.b_id];
1750 VertexBuffer& next_vbuffer = v_multibuffer[next_sub_path.first.b_id];
1751 // offset into the previous vertex buffer of the left vertex of the previous segment
1752 const size_t prev_left_offset = prev_sub_path.last.i_id - 1 * vertex_size_floats;
1753 // new position of the left vertices
1754 const Vec3f shared_vertex = extract_position_at(prev_vbuffer, prev_left_offset) + displacement_vec;
1755 // update previous segment
1756 update_position_at(prev_vbuffer, prev_left_offset, shared_vertex);
1757 // offset into the next vertex buffer of the left vertex of the next segment
1758 const size_t next_left_offset = next_sub_path.first.i_id + 3 * vertex_size_floats;
1759 // update next segment
1760 update_position_at(next_vbuffer, next_left_offset, shared_vertex);
1761 }
1762 };
1763
1764 auto extract_move_id = [&biased_seams_ids](size_t id) {
1765 size_t new_id = size_t(-1);
1766 auto it = std::lower_bound(biased_seams_ids.begin(), biased_seams_ids.end(), id);
1767 if (it == biased_seams_ids.end())
1768 new_id = id + biased_seams_ids.size();
1769 else {
1770 if (it == biased_seams_ids.begin() && *it < id)
1771 new_id = id;
1772 else if (it != biased_seams_ids.begin())
1773 new_id = id + std::distance(biased_seams_ids.begin(), it);
1774 }
1775 return (new_id == size_t(-1)) ? id : new_id;
1776 };
1777
1778 const size_t vertex_size_floats = t_buffer.vertices.vertex_size_floats();
1779 for (const Path& path : t_buffer.paths) {
1780 // the two segments of the path sharing the current vertex may belong
1781 // to two different vertex buffers
1782 size_t prev_sub_path_id = 0;
1783 size_t next_sub_path_id = 0;
1784 const size_t path_vertices_count = path.vertices_count();
1785 const float half_width = 0.5f * path.width;
1786 for (size_t j = 1; j < path_vertices_count - 1; ++j) {
1787 const size_t curr_s_id = path.sub_paths.front().first.s_id + j;
1788 const size_t move_id = extract_move_id(curr_s_id);
1789 const Vec3f& prev = gcode_result.moves[move_id - 1].position;
1790 const Vec3f& curr = gcode_result.moves[move_id].position;
1791 const Vec3f& next = gcode_result.moves[move_id + 1].position;
1792
1793 // select the subpaths which contains the previous/next segments
1794 if (!path.sub_paths[prev_sub_path_id].contains(curr_s_id))
1795 ++prev_sub_path_id;
1796 if (!path.sub_paths[next_sub_path_id].contains(curr_s_id + 1))
1797 ++next_sub_path_id;
1798 const Path::Sub_Path& prev_sub_path = path.sub_paths[prev_sub_path_id];
1799 const Path::Sub_Path& next_sub_path = path.sub_paths[next_sub_path_id];
1800
1801 const Vec3f prev_dir = (curr - prev).normalized();
1802 const Vec3f prev_right = Vec3f(prev_dir.y(), -prev_dir.x(), 0.0f).normalized();
1803 const Vec3f prev_up = prev_right.cross(prev_dir);
1804
1805 const Vec3f next_dir = (next - curr).normalized();
1806
1807 const bool is_right_turn = prev_up.dot(prev_dir.cross(next_dir)) <= 0.0f;
1808 const float cos_dir = prev_dir.dot(next_dir);
1809 // whether the angle between adjacent segments is greater than 45 degrees
1810 const bool is_sharp = cos_dir < 0.7071068f;
1811
1812 float displacement = 0.0f;
1813 if (cos_dir > -0.9998477f) {
1814 // if the angle between adjacent segments is smaller than 179 degrees
1815 const Vec3f med_dir = (prev_dir + next_dir).normalized();
1816 displacement = half_width * ::tan(::acos(std::clamp(next_dir.dot(med_dir), -1.0f, 1.0f)));
1817 }
1818
1819 const float sq_prev_length = (curr - prev).squaredNorm();
1820 const float sq_next_length = (next - curr).squaredNorm();
1821 const float sq_displacement = sqr(displacement);
1822 const bool can_displace = displacement > 0.0f && sq_displacement < sq_prev_length && sq_displacement < sq_next_length;
1823
1824 if (can_displace) {
1825 // displacement to apply to the vertices to match
1826 const Vec3f displacement_vec = displacement * prev_dir;
1827 // matches inner corner vertices
1828 if (is_right_turn)
1829 match_right_vertices(prev_sub_path, next_sub_path, curr_s_id, vertex_size_floats, -displacement_vec);
1830 else
1831 match_left_vertices(prev_sub_path, next_sub_path, curr_s_id, vertex_size_floats, -displacement_vec);
1832
1833 if (!is_sharp) {
1834 // matches outer corner vertices
1835 if (is_right_turn)
1836 match_left_vertices(prev_sub_path, next_sub_path, curr_s_id, vertex_size_floats, displacement_vec);
1837 else
1838 match_right_vertices(prev_sub_path, next_sub_path, curr_s_id, vertex_size_floats, displacement_vec);
1839 }
1840 }
1841 }
1842 }
1843 };
1844
1845#if ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1846 auto load_vertices_time = std::chrono::high_resolution_clock::now();
1847 m_statistics.load_vertices = std::chrono::duration_cast<std::chrono::milliseconds>(std::chrono::high_resolution_clock::now() - start_time).count();
1848#endif // ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1849
1850 // smooth toolpaths corners for TBuffers using triangles
1851 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_buffers.size(); ++i) {
1852 const TBuffer& t_buffer = m_buffers[i];
1853 if (t_buffer.render_primitive_type == TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::Triangle)
1854 smooth_triangle_toolpaths_corners(t_buffer, vertices[i]);
1855 }
1856
1857 // dismiss, no more needed
1858 std::vector<size_t>().swap(biased_seams_ids);
1859
1860 for (MultiVertexBuffer& v_multibuffer : vertices) {
1861 for (VertexBuffer& v_buffer : v_multibuffer) {
1862 v_buffer.shrink_to_fit();
1863 }
1864 }
1865
1866 // move the wipe toolpaths half height up to render them on proper position
1867 MultiVertexBuffer& wipe_vertices = vertices[buffer_id(EMoveType::Wipe)];
1868 for (VertexBuffer& v_buffer : wipe_vertices) {
1869 for (size_t i = 2; i < v_buffer.size(); i += 3) {
1870 v_buffer[i] += 0.5f * GCodeProcessor::Wipe_Height;
1871 }
1872 }
1873
1874 // send vertices data to gpu, where needed
1875 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_buffers.size(); ++i) {
1876 TBuffer& t_buffer = m_buffers[i];
1877 if (t_buffer.render_primitive_type == TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::InstancedModel) {
1878 const InstanceBuffer& inst_buffer = instances[i];
1879 if (!inst_buffer.empty()) {
1880 t_buffer.model.instances.buffer = inst_buffer;
1881 t_buffer.model.instances.s_ids = instances_ids[i];
1882 t_buffer.model.instances.offsets = instances_offsets[i];
1883 }
1884 }
1885 else {
1886 if (t_buffer.render_primitive_type == TBuffer::ERenderPrimitiveType::BatchedModel) {
1887 const InstanceBuffer& inst_buffer = instances[i];
1888 if (!inst_buffer.empty()) {
1889 t_buffer.model.instances.buffer = inst_buffer;
1890 t_buffer.model.instances.s_ids = instances_ids[i];
1891 t_buffer.model.instances.offsets = instances_offsets[i];
1892 }
1893 }
1894 const MultiVertexBuffer& v_multibuffer = vertices[i];
1895 for (const VertexBuffer& v_buffer : v_multibuffer) {
1896 const size_t size_elements = v_buffer.size();
1897 const size_t size_bytes = size_elements * sizeof(float);
1898 const size_t vertices_count = size_elements / t_buffer.vertices.vertex_size_floats();
1899 t_buffer.vertices.count += vertices_count;
1900
1901#if ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1902 m_statistics.total_vertices_gpu_size += static_cast<int64_t>(size_bytes);
1903 m_statistics.max_vbuffer_gpu_size = std::max(m_statistics.max_vbuffer_gpu_size, static_cast<int64_t>(size_bytes));
1904 ++m_statistics.vbuffers_count;
1905#endif // ENABLE_GCODE_VIEWER_STATISTICS
1906
1907#if ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
1908 GLuint vao_id = 0;
1909 if (OpenGLManager::get_gl_info().is_version_greater_or_equal_to(3, 0)) {
1910 glsafe(::glGenVertexArrays(1, &vao_id));
1911 glsafe(::glBindVertexArray(vao_id));
1912 }
1913#endif // ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
1914
1915 GLuint vbo_id = 0;
1916 glsafe(::glGenBuffers(1, &vbo_id));
1917 glsafe(::glBindBuffer(GL_ARRAY_BUFFER, vbo_id));
1918 glsafe(::glBufferData(GL_ARRAY_BUFFER, size_bytes, v_buffer.data(), GL_STATIC_DRAW));
1919 glsafe(::glBindBuffer(GL_ARRAY_BUFFER, 0));
1920
1921#if ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
1922 if (OpenGLManager::get_gl_info().is_version_greater_or_equal_to(3, 0)) {
1923 glsafe(::glBindVertexArray(0));
1924 t_buffer.vertices.vaos.push_back(static_cast<unsigned int>(vao_id));
1925 }
1926#endif // ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
1927 t_buffer.vertices.vbos.push_back(static_cast<unsigned int>(vbo_id));
1928 t_buffer.vertices.sizes.push_back(size_bytes);
1929 }
1930 }
1931 }

1947 for (TBuffer& buffer : m_buffers) {

1952 using CurrVertexBuffer = std::pair<unsigned int, size_t>;

1966 size_t seams_count = 0;
1967
1968 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_moves_count; ++i) {
1969 const GCodeProcessorResult::MoveVertex& curr = gcode_result.moves[i];
1970 if (curr.type == EMoveType::Seam)
1971 ++seams_count;
1972

1988 progress_dialog->Fit();
1989 progress_count = 0;

1992 const unsigned char id = buffer_id(curr.type);
1993 TBuffer& t_buffer = m_buffers[id];
1994 MultiIndexBuffer& i_multibuffer = indices[id];
1995 CurrVertexBuffer& curr_vertex_buffer = curr_vertex_buffers[id];
1996#if ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE

1998 VIndexList& vbo_index_list = vbo_indices[id];
1999#else
2000 VboIndexList& vbo_index_list = vbo_indices[id];
2001#endif // ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
2002

2004 if (i_multibuffer.empty()) {
2005 i_multibuffer.push_back(IndexBuffer());
2006#if ENABLE_GL_CORE_PROFILE
2007 if (!t_buffer.vertices.vaos.empty() && OpenGLManager::get_gl_info().is_version_greater_or_equal_to(3, 0))
2008 vao_index_list.push_back(t_buffer.vertices.vaos[curr_vertex_buffer.first]);
2009
2010 if (!t_buffer.vertices.vbos.empty())
2011 vbo_index_list.push_back(t_buffer.vertices.vbos[curr_vertex_buffer.first]);
2012#else
2013 if (!t_buffer.vertices.vbos.empty())
2014 vbo_index_list.push_back(t_buffer.vertices.vbos[curr_vertex_buffer.first]);

3742 using TimesList = std::vector<std::pair<CustomGCode::Type, Times>>;

3744 // helper structure containig the data needed to render the time items
3745 struct PartialTime
3746 {
3747 enum class EType : unsigned char
3748 {
3749 Print,
3750 ColorChange,
3751 Pause
3752 };
3753 EType type;
3754 int extruder_id;
3755 ColorRGBA color1;
3756 ColorRGBA color2;
3757 Times times;
3758 std::pair<double, double> used_filament{ 0.0f, 0.0f };

3761
3762 auto generate_partial_times = [this, get_used_filament_from_volume](const TimesList& times, const std::vector<double>& used_filaments) {
3763 PartialTimes items;
3764
3765 std::vector<CustomGCode::Item> custom_gcode_per_print_z = wxGetApp().is_editor() ? wxGetApp().plater()->model().custom_gcode_per_print_z.gcodes : m_custom_gcode_per_print_z;
3766 std::vector<ColorRGBA> last_color(m_extruders_count);
3767 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_extruders_count; ++i) {
3768 last_color[i] = m_tool_colors[i];
3769 }
3770 int last_extruder_id = 1;
3771 int color_change_idx = 0;
3772 for (const auto& time_rec : times) {
3773 switch (time_rec.first)
3774 {
3775 case CustomGCode::PausePrint: {
3776 auto it = std::find_if(custom_gcode_per_print_z.begin(), custom_gcode_per_print_z.end(), [time_rec](const CustomGCode::Item& item) { return item.type == time_rec.first; });
3777 if (it != custom_gcode_per_print_z.end()) {
3778 items.push_back({ PartialTime::EType::Print, it->extruder, last_color[it->extruder - 1], ColorRGBA::BLACK(), time_rec.second });
3779 items.push_back({ PartialTime::EType::Pause, it->extruder, ColorRGBA::BLACK(), ColorRGBA::BLACK(), time_rec.second });
3780 custom_gcode_per_print_z.erase(it);
3781 }
3782 break;
3783 }
3784 case CustomGCode::ColorChange: {
3785 auto it = std::find_if(custom_gcode_per_print_z.begin(), custom_gcode_per_print_z.end(), [time_rec](const CustomGCode::Item& item) { return item.type == time_rec.first; });
3786 if (it != custom_gcode_per_print_z.end()) {
3787 items.push_back({ PartialTime::EType::Print, it->extruder, last_color[it->extruder - 1], ColorRGBA::BLACK(), time_rec.second, get_used_filament_from_volume(used_filaments[color_change_idx++], it->extruder - 1) });
3788 ColorRGBA color;
3789 decode_color(it->color, color);
3790 items.push_back({ PartialTime::EType::ColorChange, it->extruder, last_color[it->extruder - 1], color, time_rec.second });
3791 last_color[it->extruder - 1] = color;
3792 last_extruder_id = it->extruder;
3793 custom_gcode_per_print_z.erase(it);
3794 }
3795 else
3796 items.push_back({ PartialTime::EType::Print, last_extruder_id, last_color[last_extruder_id - 1], ColorRGBA::BLACK(), time_rec.second, get_used_filament_from_volume(used_filaments[color_change_idx++], last_extruder_id - 1) });
3797
3798 break;
3799 }
3800 default: { break; }
3801 }
3802 }
3803
3804 return items;
3805 };
